        "text_KBqqfp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>High in the cliffs of Nepal, where altitude meets ancient tradition, fearless honey hunters climb the mountain cliff to harvest a wild, neuroactive honey revered for centuries. Guided by generations of knowledge and deep respect for nature, their courage brings us one of the most potent pure gold honey on earth.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
